column5: Hello  Guided a couple of days last week(sun-tues) and fished with Nancy and Ken On Tuesday afternoon  Its has been a great season, with some fresh COHO's,  BROWNS and CHINNEY'S in the mix  Since I am having troubles posting pics right on the screen (dont know how)  Here are some links   A couple smaller Chinny's  http://i172.photobucket.com/albums/w12/dma...pg?t=1190641636 http://i172.photobucket.com/albums/w12/dma...pg?t=1190641829  A dark COHO  http://i172.photobucket.com/albums/w12/dma...pg?t=1190641907  A couple of BROWNS  http://i172.photobucket.com/albums/w12/dma...pg?t=1190641968 http://i172.photobucket.com/albums/w12/dma...pg?t=1190641993 http://i172.photobucket.com/albums/w12/dma...pg?t=1190642016 http://i172.photobucket.com/albums/w12/dma...pg?t=1190642046  AND FINALY  NANCY AKA CHROME HEN  With her first and second landed fish  http://i172.photobucket.com/albums/w12/dma...pg?t=1190642383 http://i172.photobucket.com/albums/w12/dma...pg?t=1190642415  Dave
Show Off!!!   hahaha    I still laugh when I think of what I had to call you in order for you to smile big for some of those pics.  lol
Nice catch !!!!! those brown trout pics are great,love the colors too.  ...they were all very nice sized fish thanks for sharing....cheers
Great looking fish Dave, nice mix of species and I love the colours/patterns on those browns.  Thanks for sharing.
Nice whack of fish Dave  MTP
Ya just because I was violating the fish doesnt make me a bad person NANCY  Anyway It was fun and I am looking orward for TUESDAY to go again.   BOWSHEP and MILTY  get ready to rumble  Dave
